article_title: County will look at privatizing EMS, county attorney, other departments
article_text: Rob Bullock is owner/operator of Bullock Farms fish farms as well as a full-time EMT for Highlands County EMS. FILE

article_metadata.Description: SEBRING - For more than six months, local tea party members have asked the Highlands County commissioners to privatize the public ambulance service.
